{"tid":1199222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂一陣就ok] 募集想出嚟但係出唔到嘅各位巴打絲打","createTime":"2019-06-10T12:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:16:43.000Z","uid":174882,"like":268,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"504a3491b1a8d928837f1cb623e737b0d1adfb22","tid":1199222,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的  我相信聽晚好需要再直播  畀外國人睇下香港發生乜嘢事<br />\n琴晚有咁多位嘅 落力幫推  高峰曾經有1700人同時睇緊  <br />\n當中包括美國，英國，德國，瑞典，荷蘭，布里斯班嘅觀眾<br />\n淨係1700人已經成日有人問發生乜嘢事  同埋聽唔明 <br />\n亦有支持修例人士不斷作出滋擾性嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n然而我要咁多位嘅幫忙<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 如果你識得即時翻譯英文嘅</span> </strong><br />\n希望你能夠義務幫我嘅直播做英文翻譯畀外國人聽 <br />\n或者英文底好好  識好多Politics生字 <br />\n都入嚟幫下忙做提字機協助發言嗰班翻譯員<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>2. 如果你平時有睇開twitch  識得做moderator簡單嘅工作</strong></span><br />\n希望你能夠義務為我個台做管理員嘅工作 <br />\n因為我冇辦法估計今次會有幾多人入嚟睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>3. 如果你係一個好勁嘅Content Creator </strong></span><br />\n希望你能夠幫我設計一個區旗嘅gif <br />\n我將會用佢喺follower同埋host alert度 <br />\n個gif 要包含區旗同埋&quot;support HK&quot;嘅字眼 <br />\n如果得嘅話我想要支飄揚嘅區旗<br />\n歡迎將作品擺喺<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1198285/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1198285/page/1</a> 集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n呢個將會係我今次直播用嘅Discord:<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8JJDt7C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F8JJDt7C&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=bc9907be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/8JJDt7C</a><br />\n有興趣義務幫手嘅  請喺#application寫出你想做嘅嘢<br />\n其他人鍾意嘅可以入嚟吹下水 <br />\n亦都有voice channel畀你哋聽晚呻下  發表不滿嘅聲音<br />\n<br />\n如果聽晚唔同電視台都有直播 <br />\n我會喺twitch集合一次過畀外國人睇 <br />\ntwitch.tv/ronald_fung<br />\n如果直播開始咗請將佢share有幾遠得幾遠 <br />\nShare去Reddit/Twitter會多好多外國人睇到"},{"pid":"024fb4123a6e5bf0afe1412c6097f2746ed64d36","tid":1199222,"uid":174882,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"我好多謝幾個已經報咗名義務幫手嘅巴絲<br />\n同埋琴晚凌晨一點起幫手幫推嘅巴絲 <br />\n召集到1700個人睇嘅時候  我真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登真係好有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855f226a0bb4d3242fdf47f069a6d8366a868f99","tid":1199222,"uid":174882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2155623233584264cda4307260592795aea6159a","tid":1199222,"uid":174882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f7c23e9062944e9f6ca11bfee6c836001950be","tid":1199222,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9d2e8287c12dfb4487619502c628eafb9200fe","tid":1199222,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:21:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336f0ae8b40110697f8ebf56169abca7d4640fbb","tid":1199222,"uid":207208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://crowddung.firebaseapp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrowddung.firebaseapp.com%2F&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=5740184e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://crowddung.firebaseapp.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n用💩和平抗爭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb1b4c53d4b00080c81a3037b2b0142e577b5f7","tid":1199222,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285a678100d7571